{
  "stem": "3605.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But later on, in the afternoon, we realized that this was already war starting.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we all were very kind of frightened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we decided to pack our belongings and go towards Warsaw-- that maybe there is going to be a front that the Germans are not going to be able to come through so easily.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so being as we were in business, and we had those big wagons where the glass was transported from town to town, and we had four horses-- so a friend of my father took one wagon.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we, with some friends, took another wagon with-- that was like on rubber wheels where the riding was more comfortable.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we put a lot of our mobile belongings on that wagon.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we went about 35 kilometers from home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was a lot of traffic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was a fork in the road.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And one wagon went one direction.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And one wading-- wagon went the other direction.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In the same day we were minus all our belongings.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were going towards Warsaw with thousands and thousands of other people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my father, being as he dealt with a lot of people in surrounding town, had friends in each town.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Until we came to a town close by Warsaw-- and my father said, we are not going any farther, because it's going to be very, very bad with everybody going in there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was called [NON-ENGLISH], that town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is a small town before Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because my father's [NON-ENGLISH] was between Warsaw, Piotrkow, and Tomaszow Mazowiecki-- all those towns in between.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there we stood a few days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In one week, Poland was conquered till Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And later, a front was by Warsaw for weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everything was gone.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
